'''Batman''' ndi chiwonetsero chachinyengo [[Superhero|chomwe]] chikuwonekera [[Superhero|m'mabuku]] achikatolika [[Superhero|achi]] [[American comic book|America omwe]] amafalitsidwa ndi [[DC Comics]] .  Chikhalidwecho chinapangidwa ndi wojambula [[Bob Kane]] ndi wolemba [[Bill Finger]] , ndipo poyamba anawonekera ''[[Detective Comics]]'' # 27, mu 1939.  Poyambirira amatchulidwa kuti "Bat-Man", chikhalidwecho chimatchulidwanso ndi zochitika monga Caped Crusader, [[Dark Knight (nickname)|Dark Knight]] , ndi Detective Greatest Detective.

